Drop files here to have them copied onto the HDD image at build time.

Structure mirrors the FAT32 filesystem:
  rootfs/          → / (root)
  rootfs/bin/      → /bin/

Example — compile a musl program and drop it in:
  /root/NoanOS/musl-noan-cc hello.c -o rootfs/bin/hello

Then run build.sh and the binary will be on the HDD, runnable from the shell.
